NewDialogStrings.TEST_a_helpmetest: "Hey, can you help me debug something?"
NewDialogStrings.TEST_cw_starttesting: "Sure, what do you need?" {n}Woljif pauses, then adds,{/n} "You are gonna pay me for beta testing this thing, right?"
NewDialogStrings.TEST_cw_donetesting: "What else do you wanna talk about?"
NewDialogStrings.TEST_a_conditionalcue: "Let's test conditional cues. What am I?"
NewDialogStrings.TEST_a_complexconditionalcue: "Let's test advanced conditional cues. Am I both female and either tiefling or aasimar?"
NewDialogStrings.TEST_a_trueconditionalanswer: "I can see this option because I'm a tiefling!"
NewDialogStrings.TEST_a_falseconditionalanswer: "I shouldn't see this one because I'm not an aasimar."
NewDialogStrings.TEST_a_unchoosableconditionalanswer: "I can see this option but can't take it because I'm not an elf."
NewDialogStrings.TEST_sf_failedskillcheck: "Looks like you didn't pull that one off, chief."
NewDialogStrings.TEST_sp_passedskillcheck: "Hey, you did it! Good work, chief!"
NewDialogStrings.TEST_cw_falseconditionalcue: "Well, you're no tiefling, if the game logic is to be believed."
NewDialogStrings.TEST_cw_truecomplexconditionalcue: "Absolutely, and a gorgeous one at that!"
